{"title":"千年封冻的雪山下","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":2,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"千年封冻的雪山下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千年封冻的雪山下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生长着美丽的花朵；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五星红旗在雪山顶上飘扬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那花朵开得更加鲜艳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千年黑暗的部落里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枷锁着可怜的牧羊人；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产党书记来到群众中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牧人唱出了欢乐的歌声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千年茫茫的草原上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哺育着无数的牛羊；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社建立在草原中央，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那牛羊长得更加肥壮。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}